Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.19,0:01:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kursinya belum siap?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.69,0:01:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beberapa tamu mungkin membawa\Nanak-anak atau orang tua.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, saya berencana menyiapkannya...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.37,0:01:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kamu baru melapor padaku,\N"Semuanya sudah siap?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu dipecat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:01:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur, tuan muda konglomerat,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sangat membenci kebohongan dan manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.77,0:02:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pelayan robot Marie memang hebat,\Nkreasi paling membanggakan Zetes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.11,0:02:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang harus belajar dari Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.61,0:02:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, Marie sebenarnya manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika Tuan Muda tahu itu,\Nnyawanya bisa melayang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, ini kisah tentang mereka berdua.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke mana pun aku melihat,\Nsemuanya orang terkenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pesta rumah Zetes memang hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pesta rumah hari ini adalah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pesta penting yang kuadakan\Natas nama ayahku yang sedang pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai pewaris ayahku,\Naku tak boleh gagal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong serahkan\Norang mencurigakan pada saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu, itu juga penting.\NNamun, ada hal yang lebih penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:03:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong singkirkan paprika untukku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat tak suka paprika...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan membuangnya tanpa ada yang tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bibi Rustin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo, Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lama tak bertemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Auranya kuat sekali. Siapa itu?\N- Lama tak bertemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kukira dia tak dekat dengan keluarganya.\N- Syukurlah kalian tampak sehat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya Tuan Carl dan Nona Charlotte\Ndari keluarga Rustin
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang memihak Tuan Muda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak sudah datang hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.26,0:03:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan menyapa dengan kaku, Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari ekspresimu,\Nada hal baik yang terjadi, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tak bisa\Nmenyembunyikan apa pun dariku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah, katakan saja, Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata tak ada yang bisa\Nkusembunyikan darimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya kami berhasil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.09,0:03:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini robot pelayan Marie yang dikembangkan\Ndengan semua kemampuan Zetes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Robot pelayan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, manis sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan hanya kulitnya yang mulus,\Ndetailnya juga sempurna.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini cukup rumit, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tak terlihat seperti robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa ketahuan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, bersihkan piringnya.\NCepatlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, singkirkan gerobak gelas anggur ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keseimbangannya luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami memasang sistem keseimbangan juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sip, di mana Arthur?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin ada orang mencurigakan lain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata menjamu tamu itu\Nsangat melelahkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan tampak sangat lelah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski hanya ini yang bisa kulakukan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jika ini bisa menghiburnya sedikit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya tubuh Tuan sudah pulih.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya akan kembali ke tempat pesta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, tetaplah bersamaku\Nsedikit lebih lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:07:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mode saya saat ini\Nmemprioritaskan tugas pesta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mencarimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Robot, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa jantungku\Ntiba-tiba berdebar kencang?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, bawakan air untuk tamu di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku akan menyiapkan yang baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, itu teko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak apa-apa, kamu boleh pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika terus begini,\Naku akan menyusahkan Tuan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kutekan tombol detonasi ini,\NArthur akan tamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, aku bisa dapat banyak uang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tombolku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pelayan itu memukul seseorang!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Awas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Semuanya, lari!\N- Itu pelayannya, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pelayan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang harus kulakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku, pestanya jadi kacau.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf atas gangguannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pria ini sepertinya memasang bom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menakutkan sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pelayan ini telah melindungi semuanya\Ndari orang mencurigakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, Nona Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pelayan yang bisa dibanggakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Terima kasih.\N- Sangat bisa diandalkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur sangat memercayai\Nrobot pelayan itu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin dia bisa menyembuhkan\Nketidakpercayaan Arthur pada manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Robot pelayan dingin itu\Nmerusak rencanaku lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lain kali,\Naku akan membalas dendam, Arthur!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:10:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kuduga kamu akan cocok memakai\Nselain seragam pelayanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah aku memesannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah pesta berakhir,\Nakhirnya kita bisa berduaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari nikmati waktu ini bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tak menyukainya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pestanya hancur hari ini\Nkarena kelalaian saya dalam bertugas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya sungguh minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu bekerja keras seharian ini\Ndan bahkan mengurus paprika untukku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.06,0:10:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku melihat semua itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana bisa ada tuan sebaik ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Andai aku bisa melayaninya selamanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sangat beruntung.\NTak apa-apa meski tidak makan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manusia sungguh kesulitan\Ndalam mengisi ulang energi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, bagaimana caramu\Nmengisi ulang tenaga?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baterai AA... Kurasa begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang harus kulakukan?\NAku pasti akan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baterai AA, ya?\NBegitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memercayainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, sekarang,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kamu sungguh terlihat\Nseperti gadis manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana ini?\NDia pasti sudah tahu aku manusia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang bagaimana\Naku harus menghadapi Tuan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, saat itu gelap,\Njadi, dia tak melihat wajahku...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika aku berbohong dan bilang mendorongnya\Nkarena kesalahan mekanis...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkinkah Tuan sama sekali\Ntak peduli dengan kemarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia biasanya menjawabku\Ndengan "selamat pagi."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa, Marie?\NKamu tampak agak berbeda dari biasanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wajar saja dia akan curiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenanglah, aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Panik hanya akan membuatmu\Nmakin mencurigakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:12:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bilang kamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku harus menipunya!\N- Cepat, bohongi dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya tak mengerti maksud Tuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin aku bisa tahu\Nkalau mencoba hal yang sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan panik!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan, kenapa Anda tiba-tiba begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong buatkan kopi\Ndan bawakan ke ruang kerjaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu berat?\NMau kubawakan untukmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.03,0:14:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak kapan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.66,0:14:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia ingin membuktikan bahwa aku ini manusia?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terlalu dekat...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus bersikap lebih seperti robot\Ndaripada biasanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berikutnya, saya akan membersihkan\Njendela di lorong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi mesin...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi mesin...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, aku perlu bicara denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, kamu dibebastugaskan\Ndari tugas pelayanmu mulai hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mustahil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Roy, kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Muda mencurigaimu sejak kemarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika terus begini,\Nhanya masalah waktu sebelum dia tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir.\NAku akan mengurusmu mulai sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bekerjalah di tempat yang jauh dari sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kebohongan itu terungkap,\Naku tak bisa bersamanya lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan berusaha keras\Nagar tidak ketahuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Muda sungguh menyukaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, jika dia tahu,\Naku yakin dia akan sangat terluka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, pasti sulit bagimu\Nuntuk terus membohonginya seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir.\NAku sudah mengaturnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerahkan\Npeningkatan lengkap pelayan robot Marie,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}versi lebih canggih dari pelayan robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senang bertemu dengan Anda, Tuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:16:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dibangun setelah peningkatan Marie,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}saya versi lebih canggih\Ndari pelayan robot, Marie-2.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Versi lebih canggih?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya tak sabar melayani Anda, Tuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie-2 memiliki\Nkekuatan membunuh tertinggi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pelayan yang paling cocok\Nuntuk Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cocok untukku.\NBegitukah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sudah cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alat penguat bantal pangkuan Arthur\Nsudah dilengkapi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Musik putar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mobilnya sudah siap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bawa mobilnya dan pergi\Nsebelum Tuan Muda menyadarinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan mencuci seragam pelayannya\Ndan mengembalikannya padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Simpan itu sebagai kenang-kenangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kusimpan ini, aku akan sedih.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seragam ini menyimpan\Nterlalu banyak kenangan bagiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya,\Naku mau terus berada di sisinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tidak lama,\Ntapi kamu bekerja dengan baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.84,0:17:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih atas perhatianmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kuduga.\NSudah kukira ada yang aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, Roy tiba-tiba mengirim\Nrobot pelayan baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu pasti menyembunyikan\Nsesuatu dariku, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.57,0:18:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan, seharusnya\NAnda sudah punya robot pelayan baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia lebih baik dan sempurna dari saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kumohon, lupakan saja saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu memang lebih unggul daripada Marie,\Nrobot pelayan sempurna tanpa masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.97,0:18:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang janggal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu bukanlah sekadar robot biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.05,0:18:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan, saya sudah lama mencari Anda.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.21,0:18:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie-2.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pengintai tempur mendeteksi bahaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemampuan tempur amat tinggi dikonfirmasi\Ndalam radius lima meter dari Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahaya level lima.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian berdua, mundurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memulai pemusnahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Musnahkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia lebih kuat dariku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, kamu baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Punggungmu terluka...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Musnahkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tumpukan logam bekas\Nyang menyakiti tuannya
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tidak cocok menjadi pelayan Tuan Arthur!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.81,0:19:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan, punggung Anda...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak apa-apa.\NLagi pula...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, aku tahu semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alasanmu bersikap aneh belakangan ini
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.47,0:20:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena kamu rusak, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk menyembunyikannya, kamu meminta Roy\Nmenyiapkan Marie-2 untuk mengambil alih.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak peduli berapa biaya perawatannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya sudah diperbaiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sudah diperbaiki?\NCepat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika menyangkut diriku,\NTuan selalu tak tahu apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tetaplah di sisiku, Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap aku bisa selalu berada\Ndi sisi Tuan mulai sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan mengandalkanmu\Nmulai sekarang, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.85,0:21:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Banyak yang terjadi,\Ntapi berkat kamu,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.11,0:21:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku melihat Tuan Muda tersenyum\Nsetelah sekian lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai kini, aku akan bekerja lebih keras\Nsupaya tidak sampai ketahuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.91,0:21:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Satu hal lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie-2.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penyusunan ulang dan pemeliharaan selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perangkat lunak dan keras\Nsudah diperbarui ke versi terbaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini, aku mau kalian berdua\Nmelindungi Tuan Muda bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami berdua...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak sabar bekerja denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.06,0:21:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cinta segitiga antara pelayan robot asli,\NMarie-2, dan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat mereka bersaing demi kasih sayang...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.05,0:21:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu mustahil!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.97,0:22:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong pastikan kalian akur.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.70,0:23:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, kamu tak bisa diisi ulang\Ndengan baterai AA.
